{
  "stem": "19550.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something is almost impossible because of the extraordinary personality of my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would take a lifetime to describe her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I will try to compress it and still give some kind of a picture of her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was the daughter of the chief rabbi of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On her mother's side, she was a descendent of-- at least we know from the early 16th century-- of the first chief rabbi of Buda.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She was one of-- let's see-- one, two, three, four girls and two boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandfather was a very young man when he passed away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was very ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm assuming because of the descriptions that he must have had cancer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother, as a very young woman, was traveling with him from Budapest to Prague to Vienna to various experts and institutions that hopefully were going to cure him, which they didn't succeed, of course.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother's personal ambition all her life was to have become a doctor and was considered by the doctors who had met her because of her being the companion and nurse of my grandfather, apparently had unusual talents and capabilities in, in that direction.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But of course, she was not permitted to go to school and in fact, was married off early, as were the other girls, so that my grandfather would be alive and live to see the marriages of his children.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her two brothers were both rabbis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, the older brother-- I think he was the older brother-- had inherited his father's rabbinic seat.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
